Package: ldamcmc
Type: Package
Title: Markov chain Monte Carlo Algorithms for the Latent Dirichlet Allocation Model
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-11-20
Author: Clint P. George and Hani Doss
Maintainer: Clint P. George <cgeorge@cise.ufl.edu>
Description: This R package implements several Markov chain Monte Carlo (MCMC) algorithms for the latent Dirichlet allocation (LDA) mode.
License: MIT
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.2),
    Rcpp (>= 0.10.6),
    RcppArmadillo (>= 0.4.000.2),
    MCMCpack (>= 1.3-3),
    lattice (>= 0.20-29)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
